ğŸ“‹ Scoring & Debrief

After the interview:

Each interviewer completes their scorecard independently
Panel meets for structured debrief

Discrepancies are discussed and resolved
Escalate to hiring lead if needed

ğŸ’¡ Avoid groupthink by scoring independently first before discussion.
